com.yworks.yfiles.graphml

Class MapperOutputHandler<TKey,TData>

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.yworks.yfiles.graphml.AbstractOutputHandler<TKey,TData>
      • com.yworks.yfiles.graphml.MapperOutputHandler<TKey,TData>
  • Type Parameters:
    TKey - The type of the keys.
    TData - The type of the data.
    All Implemented Interfaces:
    IOutputHandler

    public class MapperOutputHandler<TKey,TData>
extends AbstractOutputHandler<TKey,TData>
    An implementation of the AbstractOutputHandler class, that uses an IMapper to retrieve the values to output for each item and a Serializer callback for the serialization or delegates to the IWriteContext.serialize(Type, IWriteContext, java.lang.Object) callback.
